        <updateDate>2018-01-24T22:00:50Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Fairness for Rural Veterans Act of 2017</b></p> <p>This bill includes construction or acquisition of a nursing home or domiciliary that has a significant need for beds and is located at least 100 miles away from the nearest existing state home facility as a priority for Department of Veterans Affairs state home facility grants to nursing homes and domiciliaries.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
